{"tid":1980465,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[番去印度食蕉啦]印度商人隔離期間試圖離港　被告認罪判囚4星期","createTime":"2020-04-20T06:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T07:18:48.000Z","uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c4f90d113e717ad5daebd51dcc30179c2c9ed2","tid":1980465,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*ZGdKPsWcg09e1yIefdBWjw.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1400%2F1%2AZGdKPsWcg09e1yIefdBWjw.jpeg&h=cd7e8ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名印度籍商人上月從土耳其來港，在香港仔一間酒店作隔離檢疫，但翌日隨即試圖經深圳灣口岸離港，被入境處人員截獲，並控予一項「未獲獲授權人員許可而離開檢疫地點」罪，為《外國地區到港人士強制檢疫規例》實施後，首位被檢控的外籍人士，被告今日在觀塘裁判法院承認控罪，被判監4星期。<br />\n<br />\n31歲被告被控於上月22日，在未獲衞生署署長授權人員許可下離開進行隔離檢疫的奧華時尚精品酒店，違反處方於在上月21日向他發出的書面檢疫命令。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，被告為印度軟件商人，過去兩年五度來港，他上月來港後，收到民政事務總署一份文件，令他誤以為是離港許可，所以離開檢疫地點，強調被告對為他人造成不便深感抱歉。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521605-20200420.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521605-20200420.htm&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPqZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=8a2328c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521605-20200420.htm&h=d301f3e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521605-20200420.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f0e48c78b52e61190bfc0929671d08842e0e3759","tid":1980465,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}